i nhà Trần</span>\n          <span class=\"lg:hidden mt-2 font-mono text-[9px] tracking-widest uppercase text-[var(--vn-gold)]\" data-kid=\"63\">Hào khí Đông A</span>\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"hidden lg:block font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-[var(--vn-gold)]\" data-kid=\"64\">Ba lần bình Nguyên Mông</span>\n        <div class=\"absolute bottom-[-1px] left-0 w-0 h-[2px] bg-[var(--vn-red)] group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-500\" data-kid=\"65\"></div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"project-row group py-10 border-b border-stone-100 grid grid-cols-[50px_1fr_auto] items-baseline gap-6 cursor-pointer relative\" data-kid=\"66\">\n        <span class=\"font-mono text-xs text-stone-300\" data-kid=\"67\">04</span>\n        <div class=\"flex flex-col\" data-kid=\"68\">\n          <span class=\"italic text-3xl font-semibold text-stone-800 font-display group-hover:text-red-600 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"69\">Việt Nam thời Đổi Mới</span>\n          <span class=\"lg:hidden mt-2 font-mono text-[9px] tracking-widest uppercase text-[var(--vn-gold)]\" data-kid=\"70\">Từ 1986</span>\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"hidden lg:block font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-[var(--vn-gold)]\" data-kid=\"71\">Từ 1986 đến hiện đại</span>\n        <div class=\"absolute bottom-[-1px] left-0 w-0 h-[2px] bg-[var(--vn-red)] group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-500\" data-kid=\"72\"></div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"project-row group py-10 border-b border-stone-100 grid grid-cols-[50px_1fr_auto] items-baseline gap-6 cursor-pointer relative\" data-kid=\"73\">\n        <span class=\"font-mono text-xs text-stone-300\" data-kid=\"74\">05</span>\n        <div class=\"flex flex-col\" data-kid=\"75\">\n          <span class=\"italic text-3xl font-semibold text-stone-800 font-display group-hover:text-red-600 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"76\">Di sản Thế giới tại VN</span>\n          <span class=\"lg:hidden mt-2 font-mono text-[9px] tracking-widest uppercase text-[var(--vn-gold)]\" data-kid=\"77\">UNESCO</span>\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"hidden lg:block font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-[var(--vn-gold)]\" data-kid=\"78\">Văn hóa & Thiên nhiên</span>\n        <div class=\"absolute bottom-[-1px] left-0 w-0 h-[2px] bg-[var(--vn-red)] group-hover:w-full transition-all duration-500\" data-kid=\"79\"></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n<section id=\"manifesto\" class=\"section-manifesto py-40 px-12\" data-kid=\"80\">\n  <div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center\" data-kid=\"81\">\n    <div class=\"space-y-4\" data-kid=\"82\">\n      <div class=\"manifesto-line-wrap\" data-kid=\"83\"><span class=\"manifesto-line italic font-black text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-display\" data-kid=\"84\">Thấu hiểu quá khứ.</span></div>\n      <div class=\"manifesto-line-wrap\" data-kid=\"85\"><span class=\"manifesto-line italic font-black text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-display\" data-kid=\"86\">Vững bước tương lai.</span></div>\n      <div class=\"manifesto-line-wrap\" data-kid=\"87\"><span class=\"manifesto-line italic font-black text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-display\" data-kid=\"88\">Lịch sử không chỉ là con số.</span></div>\n      <div class=\"manifesto-line-wrap\" data-kid=\"89\"><span class=\"manifesto-line italic font-black text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-display\" data-kid=\"90\">Đó là câu chuyện cha ông.</span></div>\n      <div class=\"manifesto-line-wrap\" data-kid=\"91\"><span class=\"manifesto-line italic font-black text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-8xl font-display text-[var(--vn-red)]\" data-kid=\"92\">Tự hào dân tộc Việt Nam.</span></div>\n    </div>\n    <p id=\"manifesto-tag\" class=\"mt-20 font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-[var(--vn-gold)] opacity-0\" data-kid=\"93\">\n      Thiết lập 2024 · 50+ Câu hỏi · AI Tích hợp\n    </p>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n<section id=\"tinh-nang\" class=